{"tid":1451993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣組］自稱美國律師喎話要止暴制亂","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:01:02.000Z","uid":289094,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c68a7fa219603774a51132ead702827797f73a0","tid":1451993,"uid":289094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:01:59.000Z","msg":"【一位香港人係美國做律師既睇法】<br />\n<br />\n世界有好多地區或國家譴責暴徒，只有黑衫人或者仲支持黑衫人士，自我感覺良好，黑衫搞到香港周圍都亂，唔好再話警察搞亂，如果唔係黑衫人阻塞馬路，整路障，噴塗鴉，警察防暴就唔會黎驅散，大家要話俾自己朋友知道「沒有暴徒黑衫人，就沒有警察防暴驅散，沒有路障阻塞馬路，就沒有催淚彈驅散」，唔好成日話年輕人為香港，宜家係年輕人搞亂香港安寧<br />\n<br />\n#大家一傳十 #香港你我都有份 #你我都年輕過但沒有破壞過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/834591649886233/posts/2669252966420083?s=688198506&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F834591649886233%2Fposts%2F2669252966420083%3Fs%3D688198506%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=5f7f3586\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/834591649886233/posts/2669252966420083?s=688198506&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n隨時係二打六"},{"pid":"0ae17a371db93ef36b158bb2399d5abb929b5d12","tid":1451993,"uid":116511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:11:28.000Z","msg":"Stop making stupid people famous"},{"pid":"a7fc21301cc3020cfc5521e71c095e4eb171c965","tid":1451993,"uid":61032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">含撚啦屌佢老母<br />\n6.9果日撤回一早就乜都完晒啦<br />\n咁撚樣既智力學人做律師，隨時又係假執業資格</span></span>"},{"pid":"6ba71449e3c6a60817b8299d0c6ed5a832b249db","tid":1451993,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:20:22.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"421b41b8b7140fe10b763ed3674b6c1297a6bd1f","tid":1451993,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"向國土安全部舉報"}]}